            Having said that, I hope that the noble Baroness will feel able to withdraw her amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0661P0-01459'>
        <a name='S5LV0661P0_20040511_GCR_48'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-sally-hamwee' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
