          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jeff-rooker" title="Mr Jeff Rooker">Lord Rooker</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The noble Lord, Lord Hanningfield, said that he was moving Amendment No. 59 and wanted to speak to Amendment No. 62; but he also mentioned Amendment No. 60.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0661P0-01562'>
        <a name='S5LV0661P0_20040511_GCR_151'>  </a>
