      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_97gc' title='Col. 97GC &mdash; HL Deb 11 May 2004 vol 661 c97GC' name='column_97gc' href='#column_97gc' rel='bookmark'>97GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-01604'>
